/// <summary>
/// Welcome to DILDO (Distributed Interface of Local Data Orchestration)!
/// 
/// DILDO is a sophisticated yet user-friendly networking solution designed for local network environments. 
/// It features a unique hybrid model that seamlessly transitions between client and server roles, 
/// providing unparalleled flexibility in managing network interactions. 
/// Built exclusively on UDP packets, DILDO ensures efficient and reliable communication within your local network infrastructure.
/// 
/// Key Features:
/// - Hybrid Model:                     Easily switch between client and server roles to adapt to changing network requirements.
/// - UDP Packet-based:                 Utilizes UDP packets for fast and efficient data transmission.
/// - Automatic Packet Serialization:   Simplifies data exchange with automatic JSON packet creation from custom classes.
/// - Versatile Packet Options:         Supports both JSON and binary packet formats to accommodate diverse project needs.
/// 
/// Whether you're developing multiplayer games, IoT applications, or any other local networking project, 
/// DILDO offers a straightforward solution for managing network communication with ease.
/// </summary>

